<lb ed="D" n="0777b04"/><p xml:id="pD48p0777b0401"><g ref="#CB28906">󷃪</g>問新到離什麼<g ref="#CB20060">䖏</g>　云雪峯来　<g ref="#CB28906">󷃪</g>云雪峯有什
